about.summary: Create Q-Q and manhattan plots for GWAS data from PLINK results.

name: r-qqman
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '0.1.4' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-qqman
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/qqman_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/qqman/qqman_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 3ad01f82132bf75960ae0d8a81cae84eaf4a9ab262f183fc3d6439189e4a3aed

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-calibrate
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-calibrate

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('qqman')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('qqman')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=qqman
  license: GPL-3
  summary: Create Q-Q and manhattan plots for GWAS data from PLINK results.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - jenzopr
